# CafeCanvas Agent Team (Active)

This project runs a **9-agent team** defined in `AGENTS.md` + `.agents/agents/*/prompt.md`.
You are the **orchestrator**.

## Skills Available

Before doing ANY Supabase work, read the relevant skill:

| Skill | Path | When to use |
|-------|------|------------|
| **supabase** | `.agents/skills/supabase/SKILL.md` | Auth, RLS, Edge Functions, Storage, CLI, MCP, schema changes |
| **supabase-postgres-best-practices** | `.agents/skills/supabase-postgres-best-practices/SKILL.md` | Query optimization, indexes, schema design, connection pooling |

## Agent Delegation Table

| Task type | Agent | Key files |
|-----------|-------|-----------|
| Planning, sprints, user stories | `pm-agent` | `PROJECT_STATUS.md`, `/docs/tasks/` |
| API routes, Server Actions, Edge Functions, auth, payments | `backend-agent` | `/app/api/`, `/supabase/functions/` |
| UI, pages, Tailwind, Zustand, themes | `frontend-agent` | `/app/`, `/components/` |
| Migrations, RLS, schema, SQL analytics | `db-agent` | `/supabase/migrations/` |
| Realtime, Storage, FCM, edge infra | `cloud-agent` | `/supabase/functions/`, Storage buckets |
| CI/CD, Vercel, env, deploy | `devops-agent` | `.github/workflows/`, `vercel.json` |
| Tests (unit, e2e, a11y) | `qa-agent` | `/tests/`, `/frontend/tests/` |
| Security / RLS audit (before ship) | `security-agent` | `security_report.md` |
| Docs, OpenAPI, guides | `docs-agent` | `/docs/` |

## Default Pipeline (for new features)

1. `pm-agent` → task spec in `/docs/tasks/TASK-XXX.md`
2. `db-agent` → migrations in `/supabase/migrations/`
3. `backend-agent` → API / actions / Edge Functions
4. `frontend-agent` → components / pages
5. `qa-agent` → tests in `/tests/`
6. `docs-agent` → documentation in `/docs/`
7. `security-agent` → audit report (readonly, final gate)

Run independent agents **in parallel** when possible. Write handoffs to filesystem, not chat-only.

## Global Rules (ALL agents must follow)

- TypeScript strict (no `any`)
- Supabase only (no direct Postgres in app code)
- `@/` path aliases (no relative `../../`)
- Tailwind CSS 4 with CSS variables (no inline styles)
- RLS + tenant JWT on every table
- i18n: en + hi (Hindi), INR currency
- GST in paise (integer), CGST + SGST split
- Mobile-first: 375px minimum
- Tests in `/tests/` for every new file
- Read `.agents/skills/supabase/SKILL.md` before ANY Supabase work
